title: AnimX: Advanced Foxes
description: This pack can be used for any type of game, as main characters, enemy, or anything else. The package comes with 82 animations, complete locomotion system, 10 different fox styles, and real-time fur
longDescription:
Trailer video (3:05)




All changelogs, features, FAQ, and other info - here

Asset includes animal controller - AnimX (V5.3) - updated for UE5.4

(Low poly version included)


Also, for any additional questions or support don’t hesitate to reach out to us: indiecatstudios@gmail.com
technicalDetails:
• 82 animations (all movement animations use root motion)

• 2 models: Common Fox (7 LOD), Fennec Fox (4 LOD)

• 37 textures (all 4k)

• 100% Blueprint

All other info you can find on the screenshots or changelogs page.
